# Force LF everywhere. Without this, Windows CI runners (core.autocrlf=true
# by default on GitHub's windows-latest image) check out text files with
# CRLF line endings, while the runner's own stdout is LF-only - so a
# byte-for-byte `diff` against sim/golden-hashes.txt fails on every line
# even though the hash values are identical (see determinism CI failure,
# session 18).
* text=auto eol=lf
